<h2 id="copyright">Copyright</h2>
<p>Many of the assets are free for both commerical and personal use. However, some of the 3D anime characters are marked ‚ÄúLimited Licence‚Äù. These have specific terms of use.</p>

<p><strong><a href="https://tips.clip-studio.com/en-us/articles/1096">What are the rules for using materials from Assets?</a></strong></p>

<h2 id="cloud-storage">Cloud Storage</h2>
<p>Clip Studio users now have <strong>10GB of free cloud storage</strong> for backing up materials &amp; files.</p>

<p><strong><a href="https://tips.clip-studio.com/en-us/series/73">How to Use the Cloud Service</a></strong></p>

